{"tid":1419902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推到民間記者會講琴日罷工！！！","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:19:38.000Z","uid":265339,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b977f3135208c11bf155d4c146dd0841a1b2c8f","tid":1419902,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:59:25.000Z","msg":"琴日俾理狗催淚彈放題搞到罷工集會失晒焦，希望民間記者會講返d人和平集會俾狗搞到變警民衝突！<br />\n<br />\n仲要希望講返民航處幾千人罷工支持！因為最有影響力既罷工真係佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好俾機會港共spin落去琴日示威者個度！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：琴日係黃大仙好地地聽緊大台講野，無啦啦食左催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民間記得會傳送門<br />\n<br />\n8月6 第一次民間記者會(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416725</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ac19b1ec2494e27a3d41e13fc5eaa95d0bfe251","tid":1419902,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52d0c7c3f618350cdaf7d7bab4d4347eac1b17aa","tid":1419902,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"ae916d8c8f83c7e461a217b4a6187ef046674cd5","tid":1419902,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:00:07.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"2f3434bb41d2fd20e7d69a4b40e9d8eddc46fa28","tid":1419902,"uid":279895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/428068461385622/?notif_id=1565060239749810&not;if_t=live_video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F428068461385622%2F%3Fnotif_id%3D1565060239749810%C2%ACif_t%3Dlive_video&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKR3udkpk2Vn